column2: SELECT p.obj,  str(p.ra,#,#) as ra,  str(p.[dec],#,#) as dec,  p.r,p.u,p.g,p.i,p.z,  p.petroR5#_g,p.petroR5#_i,p.petroR5#_r,  p.petroR9#_g,p.petroR9#_i,p.petroR9#_r,  str(p.u - p.g,#,#) as ugModelColor,  str(p.g - p.r,#,#) as grModelColor,  str(p.r - p.i,#,#) as riModelColor,  str(p.i - p.z,#,#) as izModelColor,  p.dered_g,p.dered_i,p.dered_r,  ISNULL(s.z,#) as z,ISNULL(s.zErr,#) as zErr,   p.score as score,   c.z,c.zErr into mydb.Zw3# from Galaxy as p   left outer join SpecObj as s on p.objID = s.bestObjID     join dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(#,#,#) as b on b.objID = p.objID   join Photoz as c on c.objID = p.objID    WHERE p.g < # AND p.r < # AND p.i < # AND p.z < # AND c.z > # AND c.z < # AND (p.score >= #)
